data.description: Renovated and spacious home in Cape Coral! Located in a great neighborhood convenient to countless hot-spots the City has to offer, and close to the Cape Coral Bridge to Ft. Myers.  With over 1,900 sqft inside plus a large, ~500 SF, screened-in lanai this home has a ton of space.  Included is a beautifully renovated kitchen with granite tops, tile backsplash, stainless appliances, and breakfast bar.  Updated bathrooms and flooring.  Roof replaced in 2015.  HVAC replaced in 2016.   Hot water heater in 2023. Double front door with sidelights, kitchen dining area, formal dining area.   Recently updated and painted.  Covered front porch and so much more.  Schedule your private showing today!
